Addition Game 

let's build an Addition Game :
            An interactive and beginner-friendly Addition Game built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This project helps users practice basic arithmetic in a fun and engaging way.

🚀 Features
🎲 Generates two random numbers every time the game starts
✍️ Allows users to input their answer
✅ Instant feedback on correct or incorrect answers
🔄 Restart button to generate new questions
🎨 Simple and clean UI using Bootstrap and custom CSS

