🎮 How to Play
Two random numbers will be displayed on the screen
Add the numbers and enter your answer in the input box
Click the "Check" button to verify your answer
You will see:
✅ "Congratulations! You got it right." (if correct)
❌ "Please Try Again!" (if incorrect)
Click "Restart" to generate a new question
